Please Choose a Master Password This is an important security update for your Keeper account which will increase your encryption level from 128-bit AES to 256-bit AES. This update is free, takes a few seconds and is required for ALL of your Keeper devices. When the update is finished, you will automatically be logged out of Keeper. You can then log back in for normal use.
